def affiliatePlot(df,hue,title):
  plt.figure(figsize=(14,10))
  order1 = df['account_year'].value_counts().index
  fig = sns.countplot(data = df,x='account_year' ,order = order1,hue=hue)
  fig.legend(loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(1.25, 0.5), ncol=1)
  plt.xlabel('Year')
  plt.ylabel('Count')
  plt.title(title)
  order2 = df['account_year'].value_counts()

def countPlot(df,x,xlabel,title,size):
  plt.figure(figsize=(size[0],size[1]))
  Order = df[x].value_counts().index
  sns.countplot(data = df, x = x, order = Order)
  plt.xlabel(xlabel)
  plt.ylabel('Count')
  plt.title(title)
  order2 = df[x].value_counts()

  for i in range(order2.shape[0]):
    count = order2[i]
    strt='{:0.1f}%'.format(100*count / df.shape[0])
    plt.text(i,count+1000,strt,ha='center')

def countplotWithHue(df,x,xlabel,title,size,hue):
  plt.figure(figsize=(size[0],size[1]))
  order1 = df[x].value_counts().index
  fig = sns.countplot(data = df, x = x, order = order1,hue=hue)
  fig.legend(loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(.75, 0.5), ncol=1)
  plt.xlabel(xlabel) 
  plt.ylabel('Count')
  plt.title(title)
  order2 = df[x].value_counts()

def boxPlot(df,y,x,size,xlabel,ylabel,title):
  plt.figure(figsize=[size[0],size[1]])
  sns.boxplot(data=df,y=y,x=x);
  plt.ylim(18,110)
  plt.xlabel(xlabel);
  plt.ylabel(ylabel);
  plt.title(title);
